What if I want to change the styles of child components in Angular 2?
Is that even possible?
Well, yes. 

This problem first occured to me when I had to change the colors of a component in a library that isn't mine. It would be irrational to change the CSS fo the component itself, so the best solution would be to alter its style through the parent. 

<a href="https://angular.io/">Angular 2</a> 
provides a way to do that through its 
<a href="https://angular.io/docs/ts/latest/guide/component-styles.html">deep selector</a>.

